title: Report: Maryland to fire Randy Edsall
text:
Report: Maryland to fire Randy Edsall The University of Maryland plans to fire its long-time football coach Randy Edsall, according to InsideMDSports. COLLEGE PARK, Md. (WUSA9) -- The University of Maryland plans to fire its long-time football coach Randy Edsall, according to InsideMDSports . UMD Head Coach Randy Edsall talks to the media about the Terps' upcoming battle against Ohio State and touches on his focus concerning his job security. 
The publication cites sources who say Edsall probably will not have a job after the Ohio State game this weekend. 
The Terps have struggled so far this season and, according to InsideMDSports, Edsall will be kicked out once the team enters its mid-season bye week. Read or Share this story: http://on.wusa9.com/1Lk54ry TOP VIDEOS
